	<!--===== Missile Launcher =====-->
	
	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_HOI_LauncherBase">
		<defName>GW_HOI_Gun_MissileLauncher</defName>
		<label>Missile launcher Fury pattern</label>
		<description>A Multi-shot, shoulder-fired guided missile launcher used by the Astra Militarum. A favorite of Heavy Weapons Teams, these launchers can sling a potent, high-speed missile far outside the range of hand grenades and grenade launchers.\n\nHeavy Weapons Teams aim to destroy what massive volleys of lasgun fire cannot. A direct hit from a krak missile will destroy even a Space Marine Terminator.</description>
